gomodel:SYNGO_5382  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 3, 4: mass spectrometry and immunofluorescence imaging of both synaptosomes and dopaminergic (selected by FACS) synaptosomes all showed synaptic localization for Copine7 (CPNE7).. Experimental description: M&M: \"We used a transgenic mouse line expressing cre recombinase under the control of the dopamine transporter (DAT-cre+; MGI:3770172, RRID: MGI:3770172)23, WT C57BL/6 N littermates, as well as a VGLUT1venus knock-in mouse line (MGI Cat# 5297706, RRID:MGI:5297706)58.\"\n\nantibody:\nRabbit polyclonal anti-Cpne7, OriGene, Cat# TA334534, RRID:N/A, Lot QC28458/40659" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
        dc:date           "2023-03-14" ;
